description:
Michael Walker is the last remaining Warring Angel trying to save the world from a nuclear war brought about by a gang of Fallen Angels.

This issue - This is it, the explosive over-sized series finale packed with action as Walker and Richardson conduct their final assault on the last remaining Fallen Angels as the world edges closer to a full scale nuclear Armageddon.

Dark streets, crooked alleys, the echo of gunfire...Mark Grimm is a detective hunting the criminal underworld. When his wife is kidnapped, no amount of bloodshed will stop Grimm from getting her back. In this tale, the truth will only be found when the smoke clears and the bodies are counted!

volume.name: The Last Sin of Mark Grimm

description: Hands covered with blood, Mark Grimm is tortured by the murder of his Wife. Now Grimm hunts for her killer the only way he knows; fully loaded with lead, liquor, and savage hatred. Before he can uncover the truth, Grimm must conquer a shadowy figure from his own tangled past...

volume.name: The Last Sin of Mark Grimm

description: Battered, beaten, and hell-bent on revenge, Mark Grimm's obsession with his wife's death twists him into knots. The only path to finding her murderer lies in joining forces with the evil that grips the city. Grimm's alliance with darkness consumes what's left of his soul and reveals a much darker truth...

volume.name: The Last Sin of Mark Grimm

description: Kara is tired of waiting for humanity to give up their xenophobia, but Clark's memories of Apokolips urge him to greater patience. Booster's interrogation at the hands of EarthGotv forces grows ugly.
name: Argo Part 7

description: Still recovering from the events of "Museum of Madness", DOC UNKNOWN investigates the appearance of a bizarre fighter plane in Gate City. As he unravels the mystery, they lead him into his own past and the answers as to who exactly Doc Unknown is begin to come to light. Secret origin issue!
name: Shadow of Evil

description: Armed with a silver dagger and Webley .455-caliber pistol, Joey Chapman is the latest countryman to take up the mantle of Union Jack. When undead activity is on the rise in England and a friend is felled by a vampire's bite, Union Jack takes up the trail. He must turnback the vampiric onslaught or risk the lives of all those he holds dear.
name: TPB
